  "text": "Dataset: To evaluate the capability of our trained network for solving analogy questions in the test scenarios explained above, we use a large dataset of 3D chairs [CITATION_1] as well as a novel dataset of natural images (VAQA), that we collected for solving analogy questions on natural images.",
